OL,4,Cto lowest point in two years
OL,6,FSuppliers who have not received meter
OL,7,Freadings base their bills on estimated
OL,8,Fusage, meaning households could be
OL,9,Foverpaying, while others may not be
OL,10,Fpaying enough.
OL,12,FThe difference between a week's worth
OL,13,Fof energy at the old rates compared
OL,14,Fwith a week in April was #4.65 for the
OL,15,Faverage household, Uswitch warned.
