OL,3,CHousehold energy bills about to fall
OL,4,Cto lowest point in two years
OL,6,FHowever, the regulator has also
OL,7,Fallowed a temporary additional payment
OL,8,Fof #28 a year, or #2.33 a month, to
OL,9,Fmake sure suppliers have enough funds
OL,10,Fto support customers who are
OL,11,Fstruggling.
OL,13,FThis will be added to the bills of
OL,14,Fcustomers who pay by direct debit or
OL,15,Fstandard credit and is to be partly
OL,16,Foffset by the end of an allowance
OL,17,Fworth #11 per year that covered debt
OL,18,Fcosts related to the Covid pandemic.
