OL,3,CHousehold energy bills about to fall
OL,4,Cto lowest point in two years
OL,6,FPrepayment meter customers will not
OL,7,Fhave to pay the extra charge, as many
OL,8,Fdo not build up the same level of debt
OL,9,Fas credit customers because they top
OL,10,Fup as they go, Ofgem said.
OL,12,FThe regulator also confirmed plans to
OL,13,Fset a permanent solution to prepayment
OL,14,Fcustomers paying higher standing
OL,15,Fcharges, which was removed by the
OL,16,FGovernment's temporary Energy Price
OL,17,FGuarantee.
