OL,3,CHousehold energy bills about to fall
OL,4,Cto lowest point in two years
OL,6,FOfgem said the solution must be funded
OL,7,Fby bill-payers rather than taxpayers,
OL,8,Fto maintain fairness, meaning
OL,9,Fprepayment customers will save around
OL,10,F#49 per year while direct debit
OL,11,Fcustomers will pay #10 more each year.
OL,13,FCampaigners warned that while the
OL,14,Fcosts that households pay for every
OL,15,Funit of energy they use will decrease
OL,16,F"slightly", they were still almost
OL,17,Fdouble what they were in 2021.
