OL,6,F"This means households continue to
OL,7,Fstruggle to keep themselves warm, keep
OL,8,Fthe lights on and put food on the
OL,9,Ftable."
OL,11,FWarm This Winter spokeswoman Fiona
OL,12,FWaters said: "The issue with standing
OL,13,Fcharges is that you have to pay it
OL,14,Fwhether you've used any energy or not
OL,15,Fand it continues to rise even now when
OL,16,Fthe overall price cap has reduced.
OL,17,FThere's also a huge question mark over
OL,18,Fwhat it covers and how much profit is
OL,19,Fbeing made by these network firms.
